  "texts": [
    "As we will see in the next section, they must at least go through the motions of emotivity-related behaviors.",
    "Yet, we do not want affective artificial agents to be full-blown agents.",
    "We want them to be useful tools that we can control.",
    "We do not want them to come up with their own ends, goals, or desires.",
    "Hence, the limitations that tell apart their agency from ours."
  ],
